===爆發新型冠狀病毒===
[[File:Cheung_Hong_Estate_Hong_Mei_House_Entrance_1_view_20200211.png|250px]]
在[[2019冠狀病毒病香港疫情|新型冠狀病毒在香港-{zh-hans:暴发;zh-hant:爆發}-]]期間，居於該邨康美樓A1307室的75歲男子在2020年1月30日率先確診[[2019冠狀病毒病|新型冠狀病毒肺炎]]<ref>{{cite news|url=https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%E8%A6%81%E8%81%9E/article/20200211/s00001/1581359829914/%E7%B3%9E%E6%B8%A0%E6%8E%92%E6%B0%A3%E7%AE%A1%E5%87%BA%E4%BA%8B-%E5%85%AC%E5%B1%8B%E4%B8%8A%E4%B8%8B%E5%B1%A4%E6%84%9F%E6%9F%93-%E5%B1%85%E6%B0%91%E5%87%8C%E6%99%A8%E6%80%A5%E7%96%8F%E6%95%A3-%E5%90%8C%E5%BB%883%E4%BA%BA%E7%8F%BE%E7%97%85%E5%BE%B5%E9%80%81%E9%99%A2|title=糞渠排氣管出事 公屋上下層感染 居民凌晨急疏散 同廈3人現病徵送|date=2020-02-11|accessdate=2020-02-12|publisher=明報|archive-date=2020-02-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200212152002/https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%e8%a6%81%e8%81%9e/article/20200211/s00001/1581359829914/%e7%b3%9e%e6%b8%a0%e6%8e%92%e6%b0%a3%e7%ae%a1%e5%87%ba%e4%ba%8b-%e5%85%ac%e5%b1%8b%e4%b8%8a%e4%b8%8b%e5%b1%a4%e6%84%9f%e6%9f%93-%e5%b1%85%e6%b0%91%e5%87%8c%e6%99%a8%e6%80%a5%e7%96%8f%e6%95%a3-%e5%90%8c%e5%bb%883%e4%ba%ba%e7%8f%be%e7%97%85%e5%be%b5%e9%80%81%e9%99%a2|dead-url=no}}</ref>，接著在[[2月10日|2月10日]]，居於低層的A307室，亦有62歲女子確診新冠肺炎，其兒子及媳婦亦於翌日確診<ref>{{cite news|url=https://topick.hket.com/article/2561639/%E3%80%90%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E%E3%80%91%E6%9C%AC%E6%B8%AF%E6%96%B0%E5%A2%9E7%E5%AE%97%E7%A2%BA%E8%A8%BA%E5%80%8B%E6%A1%88%E3%80%80%E5%BA%B7%E7%BE%8E%E6%A8%93%E4%BD%8E%E5%B1%A4%E6%82%A3%E8%80%85%E5%90%8C%E4%BD%8F%E7%9A%84%E5%85%92%E5%AD%90%E5%8F%8A%E5%AA%B3%E5%A9%A6%E4%B9%9F%E6%84%9F%E6%9F%93?mtc=20023|title=本港新增7宗確診個案　康美樓低層患者同住的兒子及媳婦也感染|date=2020-02-11|accessdate=2020-02-11|publisher=topick.hket.com|archive-date=2020-03-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200327232209/https://topick.hket.com/article/2561639/%E3%80%90%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E%E3%80%91%E6%9C%AC%E6%B8%AF%E6%96%B0%E5%A2%9E7%E5%AE%97%E7%A2%BA%E8%A8%BA%E5%80%8B%E6%A1%88%E3%80%80%E5%BA%B7%E7%BE%8E%E6%A8%93%E4%BD%8E%E5%B1%A4%E6%82%A3%E8%80%85%E5%90%8C%E4%BD%8F%E7%9A%84%E5%85%92%E5%AD%90%E5%8F%8A%E5%AA%B3%E5%A9%A6%E4%B9%9F%E6%84%9F%E6%9F%93?mtc=20023|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="hk01">{{cite news|title=【COVID-19．直播】兩個案住康美樓07室　袁國勇：居民要先撤離|url=https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/432804/%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E7%9B%B4%E6%92%AD-%E5%85%A9%E5%80%8B%E6%A1%88%E4%BD%8F%E5%BA%B7%E7%BE%8E%E6%A8%9307%E5%AE%A4-%E8%A2%81%E5%9C%8B%E5%8B%87-%E5%B1%85%E6%B0%91%E8%A6%81%E5%85%88%E6%92%A4%E9%9B%A2|accessdate=2020-02-11|publisher=香港01|date=2020-02-11|archive-date=2020-08-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200824020009/https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/432804/%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E7%9B%B4%E6%92%AD-%E5%85%A9%E5%80%8B%E6%A1%88%E4%BD%8F%E5%BA%B7%E7%BE%8E%E6%A8%9307%E5%AE%A4-%E8%A2%81%E5%9C%8B%E5%8B%87-%E5%B1%85%E6%B0%91%E8%A6%81%E5%85%88%E6%92%A4%E9%9B%A2|dead-url=no}}</ref>。由於07室單位共用同一條糞渠，但室內的排氣管無密封，不排除因此散播病毒，令樓上傳染樓下。為免[[沙士事件|沙士事件]][[淘大花園|淘大花園]]集體感染病毒的事件重現，政府在2月11日深夜凌晨零時決定緊急疏散康美樓與患者住在A07室的100多名居民，到凌晨3時安排小巴前往[[北潭涌|北潭涌]][[麥理浩夫人度假村|麥理浩夫人度假村]]、[[西貢區|西貢]][[北潭涌|保良局北潭涌度假營]]、[[鯉魚門度假村|鯉魚門度假村]]及[[美孚_(香港)|美孚翠雅山房]][[隔離檢疫|隔離營]]。其中5名居民有病徵，需送院隔離治療。<ref>{{cite news |title=康美樓A07室逾30單位百人隔離　2戶未現身 |url=https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200211/bkn-20200211000327967-0211_00822_001.html |accessdate=2020-02-12 |publisher=on.cc |date=2020-02-11 |archive-date=2020-02-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200215032503/https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200211/bkn-20200211000327967-0211_00822_001.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200211/CICWZMQQZG4KF46ILRXN7E6NNU/|title=【淘大2.0】青衣康美樓疑糞渠播毒！樓上樓下07室連環確診 逾百人漏夜疏散|date=2020-02-11|accessdate=2020-03-14|publisher=蘋果日報|archive-date=2020-02-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200215032500/https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200211/CICWZMQQZG4KF46ILRXN7E6NNU/|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

到2月11日，政府官方社交平台「[[添馬台|添馬台]]」公佈307室曾更換坐廁，而排氣管切斷後未有妥善密封，而出現漏氣問題。而上層1307室患者的單位坐廁沒改裝。房屋署助理署長（屋邨管理）陸慶全表示原有污水系統設計是無問題，U型隔氣管設計亦良好，故此事件不是淘大花園的翻版，他呼籲居民如果要改裝，需諮詢房屋署辦事處。而涉事單位的改裝屬違反《建築物條例》，會要求相關住戶還原排氣管。<ref name="hk01"/><ref>{{cite news |title=房署將要求戶主還原排氣管　5名康美樓居民檢驗呈陰性 |url=https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20200211/s00001/1581414379996/%E3%80%90%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E%E3%80%91%E6%88%BF%E7%BD%B2%E5%B0%87%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E6%88%B6%E4%B8%BB%E9%82%84%E5%8E%9F%E6%8E%92%E6%B0%A3%E7%AE%A1-5%E5%90%8D%E5%BA%B7%E7%BE%8E%E6%A8%93%E5%B1%85%E6%B0%91%E6%AA%A2%E9%A9%97%E5%91%88%E9%99%B0%E6%80%A7?fbclid=IwAR2ZL4Yr6gXxx0LuWlr5pAHbkYMzfD9H2OF1qUXnrys1iAEQyNc6hbLqShs |accessdate=2020-02-12 |work=明報 |date=2020-02-11 |archive-date=2020-02-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200219135158/https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20200211/s00001/1581414379996/%E3%80%90%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E%E3%80%91%E6%88%BF%E7%BD%B2%E5%B0%87%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E6%88%B6%E4%B8%BB%E9%82%84%E5%8E%9F%E6%8E%92%E6%B0%A3%E7%AE%A1-5%E5%90%8D%E5%BA%B7%E7%BE%8E%E6%A8%93%E5%B1%85%E6%B0%91%E6%AA%A2%E9%A9%97%E5%91%88%E9%99%B0%E6%80%A7?fbclid=IwAR2ZL4Yr6gXxx0LuWlr5pAHbkYMzfD9H2OF1qUXnrys1iAEQyNc6hbLqShs |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=房屋署將檢查另外三個一柱式渠管屋邨 指擅自改渠屬違例 |url=https://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1699051/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E6%88%BF%E5%B1%8B%E7%BD%B2%E5%B0%87%E6%AA%A2%E6%9F%A5%E5%8F%A6%E5%A4%96%E4%B8%89%E5%80%8B%E4%B8%80%E6%9F%B1%E5%BC%8F%E6%B8%A0%E7%AE%A1%E5%B1%8B%E9%82%A8-%E6%8C%87%E6%93%85%E8%87%AA%E6%94%B9%E6%B8%A0%E5%B1%AC%E9%81%95%E4%BE%8B |accessdate=2020-02-12 |work=頭條日報 |date=2020-02-11 |archive-date=2020-02-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200222025950/https://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1699051/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E6%88%BF%E5%B1%8B%E7%BD%B2%E5%B0%87%E6%AA%A2%E6%9F%A5%E5%8F%A6%E5%A4%96%E4%B8%89%E5%80%8B%E4%B8%80%E6%9F%B1%E5%BC%8F%E6%B8%A0%E7%AE%A1%E5%B1%8B%E9%82%A8-%E6%8C%87%E6%93%85%E8%87%AA%E6%94%B9%E6%B8%A0%E5%B1%AC%E9%81%95%E4%BE%8B |dead-url=no }}</ref>

到2月15日，全部101名A07單位的居民樣本對病毒呈陰性反應，在中午乘坐政府安排的旅遊巴由[[隔離檢疫|隔離營]]返回居所。葵青民政事務處職員在大門外向住戶派發抗疫用品。房屋署亦已檢查所有A07單位的渠管，發現小部分曾被改動，也被修正。<ref>{{cite news |title=康美樓101名撤離居民中午回家 民政處送抗疫用品 |url=https://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1701754/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E5%BA%B7%E7%BE%8E%E6%A8%93101%E5%90%8D%E6%92%A4%E9%9B%A2%E5%B1%85%E6%B0%91%E4%B8%AD%E5%8D%88%E5%9B%9E%E5%AE%B6-%E6%B0%91%E6%94%BF%E8%99%95%E9%80%81%E6%8A%97%E7%96%AB%E7%94%A8%E5%93%81 |accessdate=2020-02-17 |work=頭條日報 |date=2020-02-15 |archive-date=2020-08-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200824020009/https://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1701754/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E5%BA%B7%E7%BE%8E%E6%A8%93101%E5%90%8D%E6%92%A4%E9%9B%A2%E5%B1%85%E6%B0%91%E4%B8%AD%E5%8D%88%E5%9B%9E%E5%AE%B6-%E6%B0%91%E6%94%BF%E8%99%95%E9%80%81%E6%8A%97%E7%96%AB%E7%94%A8%E5%93%81 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

